quran[54]{c,v,t}:
  20,1,"Twa,Hha.\t(Insiguro\ty’izi\tndome\thamwe\tn’uwufise\tubumenyi\tbwazo n’Imana yonyene gusa)"
  20,2,Nti twakumanuriye iyi Qur’ani ntagatifu kugira ngo ugire amakenga
  20,3,Ahubwo ikubere ubutumwa ku bantu bayigamburukira
  20,4,N’imanurwa rivuye kuwaremye Isi n’Amajuru yadugijwe hejuru
  20,5,Niyo Mana nyene imigisha n’inganji iri hejuru y’inyegamo yiwe nyeranda
  20,6,Ibiri mu Majuru n’ibiri kw’Isi hamwe n’ibiri hagati yavyo hamwe n’ibiri hasi y’Isi vyose nirwiwe
  20,7,"Niwavuga\tkw’ijwi\trininiya\tmu\tvy’ukuri\tImana\tniyo\tifise\tubumenyi bw’amabanga hamwe nivyinyegeje cane biri mumbari"
  20,8,"Imana, ntayindi isengwa mu vy’ukuri atari yo yonyene rudende\tgusa, nayo niyo ifise amazina meza"
  20,9,Mbega warashikiwe n’ikiyago c’intumwa y’Imana Musa (iii)
  20,10,"Mugihe yabona umuriro aca abwira umuryango wiwe ati:- nimu rindire gatoyi mu vy’ukuri jewe nabonye umuriro kumbure ndaba zanira igishirira muri uwo muriro canke ndaza kuronka mwo uwundongora muri uwo muriro"
  20,11,"Mugihe yashikayo yarahamagawe abwirwa ati:- ewe Musa (iii)"
  20,12,"Ntankeka ni jewe Muremyi wawe, rero niwambure inkweto zawe mu vy’ukuri wewe uri mumwaba mutagatifu witiriwe Twuwaa"
  20,13,Nijewe nagutoye rero niwumvirize ubutumwa ushikirizwa
  20,14,"Mu vy’ukuri nijewe Mana, kuko ntayindi isengwa bimwe vy’ukuri atari jewe jenyene, rero nimunsenge kandi muhagarike amasengesho yose kandi mumpayagiza"
  20,15,"Ntankeka umusi w’umuhero w’Isi uzoshika, nanje nkaba nshaka kuwunyegeza uwo musi kubigira mpaka kugira ngo umutima w’umwumwe wese urihwe kuvyo wakoze"
  20,16,"Ntibakuzitire kuri ivyo, bamwe batavyemera nugukurikira ivyo imitima yabo yishakira, nawe ntuze urwe muruhombo"
  20,17,None ico kiri mukuboko kwawe kw’iburyo n’igiki ewe ntumwa y’Imana Musa (iii)
  20,18,"Intumwa y’Imana Musa (iii) ibishura iti:- iyi n’inkoni yanje negamira ko kandi niyo mpungurisha ivyatsi kubera ibitungwa vyanje, kandi nkayikoresha mubindi bikorwa"
  20,19,"Imana ivuga iti:- nuyite hasi iyo nkoni yawe ewe ntumwa y’Imana Musa (iii)"
  20,20,"Arayita hasi, mumwanya ica ihinduka inzoka yiruka cane"
  20,21,"Imana ivuga iti:- nuyifate iyo nzoka kandi ntugire ubwoba, ubu rero duca tuyisubiza nkuko yamye aho hambere"
  20,22,Hanyuma ukurikize ukuboko kwawe mukwaha kwawe kuzoca kuvayo kwera derere atanabi gufise kukaba ari ikindi gitangaro kuri wewe
  20,23,Kugira ngo tukwereke ibitangaro vyacu binini biniya
  20,24,"Nugende kwa Fir’auni, ntankeka niwe yarenze imbibe zagenywe"
  20,25,"Intumwa y’Imana Musa (iii) ivuga iti:- ewe Muremyi wanje nunyagurire igikiriza canje"
  20,26,Kandi unyorohereze ibikorwa vyanje wampaye
  20,27,Kandi unziturire ipfundo riri hagati y’ururimi rwanje
  20,28,Bashobore gutahura amajambo yanje nzobabwira
  20,29,Kandi ungirire umushikira nganji wo mumuryango wanje
  20,30,Mwene wanje Haruna (iii) abe ariwe mufasha wanje
  20,31,Umuhe ubushobozi bukwiye kuri we
  20,32,Kandi umushire hamwe nanje muri ubu buzi bwanje
  20,33,Kugira ngo tuguhayagize cane
  20,34,Kandi tukuvuge wewe cane na cane
  20,35,Mu vy’ukuri ni wewe utubona
  20,36,"Imana\tivuga\titi:-\tmu\tvy’ukuri\twewe\turahawe\tmuvyo ntumwa y’Imana Musa (iii).\rwasavye\rewe"
  20,37,Mu vy’ukuri twarakugiriye impuhwe ubugira kabiri
  20,38,Mugihe twereka umuvyeyi wawe ivyerekanywe
  20,39,"Yuko woshira ikibondo cawe mw’isandugu hanyuma urishire mumwonga, n’uwo mwonga uzomuta kunkengera yarwo kugira ngo umwansi wanje aze amutore n’umwansi wiwe, kandi nashizemwo urukundo ruvuye iwanje kandi umunye ibiri mumaso yanje"
  20,40,"Wibuke igihe mushiki wawe yagenda ku bantu ba Fir’auni avuga ati:- mbega ndaba menyeshe umuntu yomurera? Duca tumusubiza kwa nyoko wawe kugira ngo amaso yiwe anezerwe kandi ntagire agahinda, kandi waragandaguye umuntu duca turakurokora nako gahinda, dutako turaku gerageza kubigeragezo vyinshi hanyuma ubaho imyaka myishi n’abantu bokwa Madiani, hanyuma wagarutse ngaha nkuko vyateguwe ewe ntumwa y’Imana Musa (iii)"
  20,41,Kandi nagutoye kubera jewe ngo ube intumwa yanje
  20,42,"N’ugende hamwe na mwene wanyu mufise ivyemezo vyanje, kandi ntimuruhe mukunyibuka"
  20,43,"Nimugende kwa Fir’auni, ntankeka yarengeje akarimbi"
  20,44,Mumubwire amajambo yoroshe nkumbure yoshobora gufata ubwo butumwa canke agatinya
  20,45,"Nabo bavuga bati:- ewe Muremyi wacu mu vy’ukuri twebwe turatinya yuko atorenga akarimbi kubera twebwe canke akatwishima ko"
  20,46,"Imana ivuga iti:- ntimutinye, ntankeka ni jewe ndikumwe namwe kuko ni jewe numva kandi mbona"
  20,47,"Rero ni mugende iwe kandi mumubwire muti:- mu vy’ukuri twebwe turi intumwa z’Umuremyi wawe, rero n’ubareke abo bene Israeri tujane nabo kandi ntubahane, mu vy’ukuri tukuzaniye ibimenyetso bivuye k’Umuremyi wawe, n’amahoro azoba ari ku bantu bakurikira uburokoke"
  20,48,Mu vy’ukuri twazaniwe ubutumwa yuko ibihano bizoshikira bamwe bahakana aya majambo y’Imana y’ukuri n’ukuyaha umugongo
  20,49,"Fir’auni avuga ati:- Umuremyi wanyu ni nde ewe Mussa"
  20,50,"Intumwa y’Imana Musa (iii) amwishura ati:- Umuremyi wacu nurya yahaye ikintu cose ishusho ryaco bwite hanyuma arakirongora"
  20,51,"Avuga ati:- mbega ni gute bamyeho mubinjana vyaho hambere mukahise utarashika"
  20,52,"Avuga ati:- ubumenyi bwivyo vyose buri k’Umuremyi buri mugitabu cayo, Umuremyi wanje atazimira canke atibagira"
  20,53,"Ariyo yabagiriye iy’Isi kuba ubusaswa nukuba girira muriyo amayira hamwe nukuba manurira amazi avuye mubicu, no kuriyo twanagishijeko ubwoko bw’imbuto zitandukanye"
  20,54,"Nimufungure kandi murishe ibitungwa vyanyu, ntankeka muri ibi vyose harimwo ibimenyetso ku bantu bafise ubwenge"